The evidence with the title 'Why Donald Trump can lie and no one seems to care ' says May 13, 2016  ... Okay , to be a bit less Trumpian about it, he has trouble with the truth. If you look at Politifact , the Pulitzer Prize-winning site that examines candidates' pronouncements for accuracy , 76 percent of Trump's statements are rated either “ mostly false, ” “ false, ” or “ pants on fire, ” which is to say off-the-charts false. 
